Name: SAMOSBOR 2D
About the game: 'SAMOSBOR 2D' is a side-shooter platformer in which you have to shoot a lot of enemies at the levels of a huge building. Solve puzzles to successfully complete levels. Collect weapons and equipment to effectively resist hordes of bloodthirsty monsters. Survive - the main goal. Game features: - Large and intricate levels, for the passage of which it is necessary to solve many puzzles; - Different types of enemies with unique combat skills; - A huge set of weapons and equipment to choose from, each of which has a different technical characteristics; - Game Mode: Survival.
